data.description: Charming home with untapped potential!  This diamond in the rough awaits your creative vision and TLC to shine once again. Boasting a spacious layout and solid bones, this property offers the perfect canvas for those eager to craft their dream space. A unique opportunity for homeowners and investors alike. Come envision the possibilities and make it yours! Located just minutes from the highway, local shops, parks, restaurants and schools, this home offers convenience. Don’t miss out on the opportunity to call 312 Lawndale Ave your new property.See agent only remarks.
